    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1952-01-07T18:50:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1952-01-07T18:50:00-05:00" n="301"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d301">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">320/12–2251: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        United States Representative at the United Nations</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Austin</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                        <lb/>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">priority</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1952-01-07T18:50:00-05:00"
                            >January 7, 1952—6: 50 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <gloss target="#t_Gadel2">Gadel</gloss> 624. <gloss target="#t_Dept1"
                        >Dept</gloss> still considering future tactics membership question. <gloss
                        target="#t_FYI1">FYI</gloss> we see serious objections to procedure (<gloss
                        target="#t_Delga1">Delga</gloss> 799, Dec 22) whereby US wld use no
                    influence prevent adoption Sov omnibus Res and abstain.</p>
                <p>Request Del’s estimate re probable date <gloss target="#t_SC1">SC</gloss> action
                    membership.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Acheson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
